        <div class="track-section">
            <h4>INPUTS WE TRACK (Not Proprietary Weightings)</h4>
            <div class="track-grid">
                <div>
                    <strong>On-Chain Fundamentals</strong>
                    Fees, revenue, DAU/MAU, TVL, take rate, token incentives, treasury runway, developer activity
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Valuation Metrics</strong>
                    P/F ratio, P/S ratio, FDV/circulating, sector comparables, revenue multiple trends
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Microstructure Data</strong>
                    Funding rates, open interest, liquidation history, exchange netflows, whale wallet tracking
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

